            </section>
        </article>

        <article class="quote">
            <h3 class="quote-title">Quote 2</h3>
            <blockquote class="quote-text">"All we have to decide is what to do with the time that is given to us."</blockquote>
            <section class="blacklist-reason">
                <h4>Reden van blacklist:</h4>
                <p>Deze quote is te filosofisch en leidt af van de gameplay.</p>
            </section>
        </article>

        <article class="quote">
            <h3 class="quote-title">Quote 3</h3>
            <blockquote class="quote-text">"A wizard is never late, nor is he early. He arrives precisely when he means to."</blockquote>
            <section class="blacklist-reason">
                <h4>Reden van blacklist:</h4>
